SpendSmart Networks Inc.


            
            SpendSmart Networks, Inc. focuses on connecting merchants and consumers through its suite of services that includes digital engagement and mobile marketing.The company's mobile loyalty solution is focused on mobile marketing for small and medium sized businesses. SpendSmart Networks was founded by Alex Minicucci on May 14, 1990 and is headquartered in San Luis Obispo, CA.

            
            (See Full Profile)


  



 


